# Intuition
At each Node in the tree, you have the option to continue the pattern and go right/left accordingly or start a new path with length 1 to the opposing direction.

# Approach
- The `length` argument is passed by value, and at any point in the recursion stack will contain the current maximum length of zigzag pattern.
- We don't need to compare the recursive call answers, so just the maximum `length` at any point contains the answer.
- We need to start the recursion call from both left and right at the root.


# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(n)

- Space complexity:
O(n): All nodes are visited once as the recursive call structure is unique.

