**Solution,**
Hum pure tree ko traverse karenge using post order traversal kyu ki agar humare pass left aur right ka information nahi aayega tab tk hum apne current node ke value ko undono se compare nahi kr payenge
Maan lo ki humara current node apne subtree ka root node hai
Hum is node ke liye kuch chize pata krni hogi

**1. Iss subtree Ka Sum 
