ye sari information ko hum ek vector ke through return karenge harr ek node ke liye.

Hum recursion ke through hrr ek node ke left subtree aur right subtree ke liye ye sari 4 information nikalnege

1. Aur uske baad hum ye check karenge ki kya iska left subtree ya right subtree BST hai ya nahi.
