**Agar ye dono cases true hote hai then hum ye kah sakte hai humara current BST ka part hai aur hum iss subtree ke sum ko apne ans variable se compare krke answer store kr lenge aur agar BST ka part nahi hua to hum iss case mai answer ko compare nahi karenge .** 


**Aur iss subtree ke liye return karenge,**
